Pretty simple install instructions. 
Make sure you have tcl8.5 installed. 

git clone https://github.com/SebLemery/eggdrop.git
cd eggdrop
./configure
make config
make; make install
cd ..
then copy simple.conf from the scripts folder to the home folder of your bot 
(where eggdrop.conf is)
edit the config file simple.conf
then start the bot: ./eggdrop -m eggy.conf
Then on IRC: /msg <botnick> hello 
